                                   'sentence_number' => 4,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '340'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Morocco is the ideal country to launch a message of peace to the Muslim world.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 5,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '341'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'A peace loving country with a respected voice in the region, Morocco is a long time friend of the United States and would be proud to host President Barack Obama in this historical event.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 6,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '342'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Eventually, and to the big disappointment of many Moroccan Obama enthusiasts, the American President did not speak in Morocco but preferred - logically, some would argue - Cairo, Egypt.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 7,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '343'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'The blogoma (acronym for Moroccan blogosphere) and many Moroccan Twitter users reacted differently to the Cairo speech.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 8,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '344'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'This is a run down of some of the reactions.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 9,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '345'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Eagerly Awaited The Obama Cairo speech was quite anticipated.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 10,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '346'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'af',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "\x{201c}What if I met Obama?\x{201d} wonders Mohamed Malouk.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 11,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '347'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'ar',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Blogging on Elmafjoue [Ar], he says: \x{644}\x{648} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62a}\x{642}\x{64a}\x{62a} \x{623}\x{648}\x{628}\x{627}\x{645}\x{627} \x{641}\x{633}\x{623}\x{637}\x{644}\x{628} \x{645}\x{646}\x{647} \x{623}\x{646} \x{64a}\x{642}\x{62a}\x{637}\x{639} \x{645}\x{646} \x{648}\x{642}\x{62a}\x{647} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62b}\x{645}\x{64a}\x{646} \x{62c}\x{632}\x{621}\x{627} \x{64a}\x{62e}\x{635}\x{635}\x{647} \x{644}\x{62d}\x{643}\x{627}\x{645}\x{646}\x{627} \x{627}\x{644}\x{645}\x{64a}\x{627}\x{645}\x{64a}\x{646} \x{644}\x{64a}\x{645}\x{62d}\x{648} \x{639}\x{646}\x{647}\x{645} \x{623}\x{645}\x{64a}\x{62a}\x{647}\x{645} \x{641}\x{64a} \x{641}\x{646} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62a}\x{639}\x{627}\x{645}\x{644} \x{645}\x{639} \x{627}\x{644}\x{634}\x{639}\x{648}\x{628} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{644}\x{64a}\x{644}\x{642}\x{646}\x{647}\x{645} \x{628}\x{639}\x{636}\x{627} \x{645}\x{646} \x{623}\x{628}\x{62c}\x{62f}\x{64a}\x{627}\x{62a} \x{627}\x{644}\x{64a}\x{645}\x{648}\x{642}\x{631}\x{627}\x{637}\x{64a}\x{629} \x{627}\x{644}\x{648}\x{627}\x{636}\x{62d}\x{629} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{644}\x{64a}\x{639}\x{644}\x{645}\x{647}\x{645} \x{643}\x{64a}\x{641}\x{64a}\x{629} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62a}\x{62e}\x{644}\x{635} \x{645}\x{646} \x{639}\x{642}\x{62f}\x{629} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62a}\x{62e}\x{648}\x{641} \x{645}\x{646} \x{627}\x{644}\x{645}\x{648}\x{627}\x{637}\x{646}\x{64a}\x{646}.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 12,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '348'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'If I met Obama, I would ask him to dedicate some of his precious time to our leaders so he could erase their ignorance when treating their people and teach them some basics of democracy and how to get rid of this fear they have of their own people.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 13,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '349'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'ar',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Mohamed [Ar] continues: \x{644}\x{648} \x{627}\x{644}\x{62a}\x{642}\x{64a}\x{62a} \x{623}\x{648}\x{628}\x{627}\x{645}\x{627} \x{644}\x{642}\x{644}\x{62a} \x{644}\x{647} \x{625}\x{646} \x{633}\x{644}\x{641}\x{643}\x{645} \x{645}\x{627} \x{62a}\x{631}\x{643} \x{641}\x{64a}\x{646}\x{627} \x{625}\x{644}\x{627} \x{62d}\x{642}\x{62f}\x{627} \x{645}\x{62a}\x{635}\x{627}\x{639}\x{62f}\x{627} \x{644}\x{623}\x{645}\x{631}\x{64a}\x{643}\x{627} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{645}\x{627} \x{623}\x{646}\x{62a}\x{62c} \x{644}\x{646}\x{627} \x{625}\x{644}\x{627} \x{63a}\x{636}\x{628}\x{627} \x{639}\x{644}\x{64a}\x{647}\x{627} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{645}\x{627} \x{635}\x{646}\x{639} \x{628}\x{64a}\x{646}\x{646}\x{627} \x{625}\x{644}\x{627} \x{643}\x{631}\x{647}\x{627} \x{644}\x{647}\x{627} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{627}\x{646}\x{62a} \x{62c}\x{626}\x{62a} \x{645}\x{646} \x{643}\x{644} \x{641}\x{62c} \x{639}\x{645}\x{64a}\x{642} \x{628}\x{623}\x{645}\x{644} \x{648}\x{623}\x{637}\x{644}\x{642}\x{62a} \x{644}\x{643}\x{644} \x{641}\x{626}\x{629} \x{648}\x{639}\x{62f}\x{627} \x{60c} \x{648}\x{627}\x{644}\x{639}\x{631}\x{628} \x{648}\x{627}\x{644}\x{645}\x{633}\x{644}\x{645}\x{648}\x{646} \x{642}\x{648}\x{645} \x{62a}\x{62a}\x{62d}\x{648}\x{644} \x{639}\x{646}\x{62f}\x{647}\x{645} \x{628}\x{64a}\x{646} \x{644}\x{62d}\x{638}\x{629} \x{648}\x{623}\x{62e}\x{631}\x{649} \x{627}\x{644}\x{622}\x{645}\x{627}\x{644} \x{625}\x{644}\x{649} \x{622}\x{644}\x{627}\x{645} If I met Obama, I would tell him that his predecessor left us with an ever growing hatred for America and that that only produced anger against it; a hatred cultivated amongst us; then you came out [President] with a deep hope and gave promises to every community whilst Arabs and Muslims usually see their hopes transform into pains.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 14,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '350'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Live-coverage One of the innovations made by the Obama administration was the possibility for members of the public to follow the Cairo speech through quotes sent by SMS text messages.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 15,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '351'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'The speech was a hot topic on Twitter where many live reactions were reported.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 16,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '352'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Larbi_org [Fr] followed the event and he twittered: Great and important speech of Obama in Cairo.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 17,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '353'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Although, Larbi later on, in a second tweet, wondered \x{201c}What did Obama mean by \x{2018}Muslim World\x{2019} ?\x{201d}.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 18,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '354'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'They were also some funny reactions when @annouss re-twitted @mbaa...',
                                   'sentence_number' => 19,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '355'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'To all people inside Cairo university, Obama is not Husni Mubarak, you don\'t have to clap on each sentence.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 20,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '356'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Analysis Citoyen Hmida has compared Cairo speech to the JFK's \x{ab}Ich bin ein Berliner\x{bb} speech.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 21,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '357'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'fr',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "He stated [Fr]: Le discours prononc\x{e9} \x{e0} l\x{2019}Universit\x{e9} du Caire a \x{e9}t\x{e9} ponctu\x{e9} par de nombreux applaudissements.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 22,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '358'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'fr',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "En effet, le fait d\x{2019}entendre un pr\x{e9}sident am\x{e9}ricain dire \x{ab} Assalamou 3alienkoum \x{bb} peut redonner espoir.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 23,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '359'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'fr',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Cette formule rappelle le fameux \x{ab} Ich ben ein Berliner \x{bb} clam\x{e9} par J.F.K. lors de sa visite \x{e0} Berlin-Ouest en juin 1963.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 24,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '360'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'fr',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Obama a eu \x{e9}galement l\x{2019}\x{e9}l\x{e9}gance intellectuelle de citer, fort \x{e0} propos, certains versets du Coran.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 25,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '361'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'The speech delivered at the University of Cairo was punctuated by much applause.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 26,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '362'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "The fact of hearing the American President saying \x{ab}Assalamou Alaykoum\x{bb} can give hope.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 27,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '363'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "This formula reminds the famous \x{ab} Ich ben ein Berliner \x{bb} stated by JFK when he visited Berlin in June 1963.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 28,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '364'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Obama had also the intellectual elegance to quote certain verses of the Quran.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 29,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '365'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'fr',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Citoyen Hmida also wrote : (...)ce discours tant attendu n\x{2019}est en partie qu\x{2019}un tissu de lieux communs sur la civilisation arabo-musulmane et sur les positions am\x{e9}ricaines contre \x{ab} l\x{2019}extr\x{e9}misme violent \x{bb}.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 30,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '366'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "This long awaited speech has been, in part, a string of platitudes about the Islamic-Arabic civilization and about the American condemnations of \x{201c}violent extremism.\x{201d}",
                                   'sentence_number' => 31,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '367'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Abdoukili reacts in a similar manner.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 32,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '368'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "The words Obama used like quotations from the Koran (to which he referred four times) and Islamic expression like \x{201c}assalaamu alaykum\x{201d} , \x{201c}azaan \x{201d} and \x{201c}Mohammed (peace be upon them) \x{201d} is a good public relation strategy to have more effect on the Muslim audience.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 33,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '369'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Wait and see Some other bloggers, even when they appreciated the Obama speech have adopted a \x{ab}wait and see\x{bb} position.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 34,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '370'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Laila Lalami , a Moroccan author based in the US wrote :',
                                   'sentence_number' => 35,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '371'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'One important test of this new approach, to my mind, is the settlements.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 36,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '372'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "Obama has already told Netanyahu that he wants a complete stop to Israeli settlements and that he won\x{2019}t accept \x{201c}natural growth\x{201d} exceptions.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 37,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '373'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => "If he can do that, then this speech will be remembered as a turning point; if he can\x{2019}t, then it will go the way of all the speeches by the previous five administrations: nowhere.",
                                   'sentence_number' => 38,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '374'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'The Skeptic But not everybody was impressed by Obama\'s words.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 39,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '375'
                                 },
                                 {
                                   'db_row_last_updated' => '2015-01-17 02:35:12.884747-05',
                                   'language' => 'en',
                                   'media_id' => 1,
                                   'publish_date' => '2009-06-08 16:27:40',
                                   'sentence' => 'Abdelhak al\'Koush , blogging on Afinina [Ar], launched a strong attack on the American president and questioned his motives in a discourteous post.',
                                   'sentence_number' => 40,
                                   'stories_id' => 7,
                                   'story_sentences_id' => '376'
                                 },
                                 {
